#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-swappo.1.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>swappo</command> <group><option><replaceable>filename.po</"
"replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>swappo</command> <group><option><replaceable>nazivdokumenta.po</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-swappo.1.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-swappo.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>swappo</command> reads the given PO-file and swaps the msgid and "
"msgstr fields for every message. The result is a new PO-file that translates "
"in the opposite direction. For example, if PO-file translates from English "
"to French, the new PO-file will translate from French to English."
msgstr ""
"<command>swappo</command> učitava navedeni Po-dokument i mijenja msgid i "
"msgstr polja za svaku poruku. Rezultat je novi Po-dokument koji prevodi u "
"suprotnom smjeru. Na primjer, ako PO-dokument prevodi sa engleskog na "
"francuski novi PO-dokument će prevoditi sa francuskog na engleski."

#. Tag: para
#: man-swappo.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new PO-file will be written to standard output. The old PO-file will "
"remain untouched."
msgstr ""
"Novi PO-dokument će biti ispisan na standardnom izlazu.Stari PO-dokument će "
"ostati nepromijenjen."

#. Tag: para
#: man-swappo.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
